Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:09.40,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,When watching Hayate no Gotoku, make sure to watch at a good distance away from the TV in a well lit room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.05,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:13.56,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:17.06,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who dedicates himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:22.88,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is a formal guardian who supports the days of their master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:25.22,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:32.84,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This is a super combat battle story of a boy who fights, risking his life for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:37.15,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thank you for watching Hayate no Gotoku again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:39.15,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's sing the opening song together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:32.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Nishizawa-san is doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:53.36,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,One family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:06.90,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Five or six customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:19.96,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Two couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:33.26,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,One old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.35,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:00.09,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.45,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:04.30,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:13.14,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Anmitsu with cream, egg stew, tokoroten, kuzu mochi, abekawa mochi, isobe yaki, inaka zenzai, and a cream soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:13.14,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Note: These are all sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.20,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,All of those, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.17,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:22.14,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Hayate-kun's doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.90,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, what did Nishizawa-san come here for the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.23,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,I shall... {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:51.20,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Lick her all over! {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.14,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun! {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:57.69,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ina**ma Kick! {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:03.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Nishizawa-san? {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.48,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're here. {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:09.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And then there was the quarrel with Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:26.70,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady and Nishizawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.01,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:34.51,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:45.56,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Nishizawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.24,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Hayate-kun! {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:06:00.01,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say goodbye like this. {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.57,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,So please go out with me! {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:08.51,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I don't have the right to date any girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:10.70,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um...{ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:15.29,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...{ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:18.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,...only interested in 2-D girls. {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:19.76,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Gahhh!!! {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.23,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I should have said no in a better manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:28.54,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!!! {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:35.63,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what I'm supposed to do in times like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.34,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And, why did Milady's face come to mind then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.76,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:47.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:51.50,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A delivery for you, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.93,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Will you open it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:59.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:05.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You are a girl, so please don't read books in that manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.27,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:11.49,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I bet an older brother worrying about his little sister must feel like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I won't find a girlfriend for a while at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.01,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,My hands are full with Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:18.39,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:20.99,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a document from Hakuou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:24.26,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's a transfer form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:24.82,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.31,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So it's for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:34.10,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it's a transfer form so you can enroll into Hakuou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:37.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard anything about that! Anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.67,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't told you anything about it before, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:42.92,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But I dropped out of my other school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.41,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I knew of that a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:49.04,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I have that school's documents in hand, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.98,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,See? Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:55.17,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But what am I going to do about tuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.27,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the economical backing to afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:02.43,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? Of course, I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.03,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,B-But.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.63,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:10.87,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to go to school with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:16.57,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,And this is like a thank you to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:18.55,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:23.24,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I can go to school again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:25.42,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.06,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.43,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Because... Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.22,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to make him cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:35.58,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't make him cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.10,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,He started crying on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:50.01,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,After reading this, it appears he has to take a transfer exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:54.13,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to claim to be a Sanzenin butler,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:57.62,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,then you'll have to pass Hakuou's transfer exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.02,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, Klaus-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:01.51,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:04.09,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't go killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:08.54,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,So, if he can't pass the exam, he'll also be fired as a butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.52,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.46,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,After having so much done for me, if I can't pass it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:21.02,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be too ashamed to be a butler... much less a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:26.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So observe everyone! What I can do when I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:30.48,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,For your information, Hakuou's standard score is just over 65.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.97,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.32,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, the exam is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the useful information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:48.54,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But will Hayate-kun really be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:53.27,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing his grades from his last school, he's right on the cutoff line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.11,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What's Hayate doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.08,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,He's studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.55,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:16.63,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.54,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,How is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.07,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.54,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't stress over it so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.01,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:38.99,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Maria-san said, I'll call it a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.35,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chief Butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:52.98,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Please wake up! This is my bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:57.40,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.74,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's not morning, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Please get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.61,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki Hayate-kun, you misunderstand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:11.72,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to enter Hakuou Academy, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:15.88,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to pass tomorrow's transfer exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:17.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:20.28,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Do my eyes look like they're lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.30,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You're scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.32,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:30.96,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,If you're thinking of my welfare,\Nthen please leave and let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:35.54,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to tell you my application process story because I care about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.28,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly reject your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.01,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:41.77,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being nonsensical!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:45.60,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't want to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.49,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... He started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:45.60,Default-alt,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,It was when I applied to a prestigious private kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:52.74,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,There was a problem I couldn't solve no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:56.43,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,The time limit was approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:59.08,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, I couldn't solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.90,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,And right when the time was about to run out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:16.01,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-kun, you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:20.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So the lesson is to never give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.23,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.93,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:45.88,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Teretemasu, hisabisa no deban de
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.88,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Teretemasu, hisabisa no deban de = I'm blushing because I got some screentime
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:50.82,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Deluxe animation, Tama no otaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:50.82,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Deluxe animation, Tama no otaku! = Deluxe animation, Tama's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:02.93,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Sine, cosine, tangent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:05.14,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they'll come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.26,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:10.60,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Tama! Where did you come in from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:17.80,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what Hakuou's exam style and questions are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:22.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be taught by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.15,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.52,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.68,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.96,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry. Sleep tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.71,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.30,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.37,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only lacking a bit of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.00,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A train?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.91,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's because the campus is so large.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:39.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I've done the best I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.63,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of questions I'll get.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.73,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be English and such, like any other place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:49.97,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think you'll pass using Moe-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:59.40,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,You think Hakuou Academy's transfer exam is something ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.21,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.73,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, former intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.72,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,And Nagi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:12.37,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm today's proctor, the beautiful world history teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.72,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Katsura Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:17.33,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,"B-Beautiful?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.50,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Don't question that word!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:25.74,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Not ordinary? But I took an ordinary exam when I entered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:32.51,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,If you rely on the past, you won't gain anything in the future, Nagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.30,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure about only looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:39.88,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll start the transfer exam, so follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:43.72,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,The topic is... the Redmond-style interview exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.93,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Redmond-style interview exam is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.40,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...a popular exam style during job interviews...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:56.37,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...to see the candidate's true intelligence through logic questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:00.43,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,"Why is a manhole cover round?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:03.23,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It's an exam that doesn't rely on memorization...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.07,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...and tests only the intelligence by asking....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:08.55,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...and answering peculiar questions and so on, as logically as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:12.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This sure is the famous Hakuou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.85,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The exam style is unique on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:18.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why is a manhole cover round?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:21.65,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Because if it's square, a slight tilt will make it fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:28.14,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The length of a diagonal in a square is longer than its sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.48,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Whereas a circle doesn't have that problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.84,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:43.09,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously. I don't go to Hakuou for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:50.14,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's start the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.49,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be inside this classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.82,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,The test begins the moment you step in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:59.23,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you do or say in here affects your score.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:01.51,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:06.34,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Question one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.17,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.22,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:26.25,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Or are teachers forgiven no matter what they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.43,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, your jabs are brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:34.83,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But! This is Hakuou Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:40.30,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,And, this is a Redmond-style interview exam that tests true intelligence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:44.65,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to, go ahead and answer the question as you imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.78,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if that's the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:50.80,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:56.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,At a glance, this is an intelligence test where\Na monkey has to get the banana using tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:03.50,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But in Redmond-style interview exams,\Nusually the first thing that comes to your mind is incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:04.38,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.60,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:13.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The point to this question is the height at which the banana is hung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:19.18,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The banana is actually at a height low enough to reach by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:23.18,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore all the tools around it are just to fool you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:30.12,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,and the answer is to take it without using any of the tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.11,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This is the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:48.81,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The one and only food for the monkeys that couldn't get the food and are starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:54.55,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh damn it, so that's how you play it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:19:01.77,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. So I get to become red all over after these long, peaceful days?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:05.12,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:08.73,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't beat this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:13.40,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.21,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.87,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,So he fights rather than running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:30.01,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,This is animal abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:35.91,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But, wow, your butler puts up a good fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:38.54,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Well, his life depends on this exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.02,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:48.87,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's end the joke here and get the real exam started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.50,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What?! This was a joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:56.08,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! If you can test for intelligence with an exam like this, then where's the effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.97,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then what was all of this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:03.91,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,As a token of my thanks, I thought I'd let you loosen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:06.15,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need this kind of thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:13.70,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And so Hayate takes the exam\Nphysically and mentally beaten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:17.38,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Calm down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.28,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to answer all the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:31.59,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But if I didn't pass it after all you've done for me, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:35.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being so pessimistic now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.13,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.34,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You're the person I have faith in, {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.56,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,so let's go to school together. {ep 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:51.86,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.61,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, Superindendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:04.59,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to send this to Sanzenin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:08.15,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But... Superindendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:13.11,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Is it correct to assume you made a typo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:19.10,Default,Pres,0000,0000,0000,,He was a point away from the passing line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.20,Default,Pres,0000,0000,0000,,He almost made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:23.36,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:28.93,Default,Pres,0000,0000,0000,,If he had answered more calmly, he might have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.16,Default,Pres,0000,0000,0000,,He was really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.28,Default,Pres,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:38.36,Default,Pres,0000,0000,0000,,I leave you to your task, Katsura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:44.58,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, at the Sanzenin's,\Nwhere they don't know what's to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:47.79,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's little early, but let's start the celebration party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:49.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:50.53,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:53.64,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...they're already in a party mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.25,0:23:31.22,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:32.24,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:33.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:36.86,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, was studying for the test fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.13,0:23:39.99,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was able to enjoy the mood of a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:41.62,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.62,0:23:43.00,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No need for that, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.28,0:23:45.95,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to go to school together every day from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:47.98,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:51.59,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be goodbye to your all-night online gaming life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:52.81,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:53.64,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:57.21,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I know! You can skip school with me from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:23:58.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ehhh?!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:23:59.72,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:03.80,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I meant it as a prank! I meant it as a simple joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.80,0:24:06.49,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought he'd fail by just one point!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.49,0:24:08.86,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,So you want me to go apologize with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.86,0:24:10.75,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.75,0:24:13.49,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Today's party will be a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.49,0:24:16.35,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,It's all for he who was admitted to Hakuou.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.63,0:24:19.21,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Hayate no Gotoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.21,0:24:22.51,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a Moment! I Have to Go to the Party. Make It Fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.51,0:24:25.74,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,This situation makes it harder to bring the issue up than I'd thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.74,0:24:27.38,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Apocalyptic destiny.
